import React from 'react';
import { View, Dimensions } from 'react-native';
import Svg, { Path, Rect, Defs, LinearGradient, Stop, Text } from 'react-native-svg';

const OctahedronSvg = ({ width = 60, height = 60, style, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <View style={[
      {
        width: width,
        height: height,
        aspectRatio: 1,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
      },
      style
    ]}>
      <Svg
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
        viewBox="0 0 492 467"
        preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
        fill="none"
        {...props}
      >
        <Defs>
          {/* Subtle edge glow */}
          <filter id="edgeGlow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceAlpha" stdDeviation="2" result="blur"/>
            <feFlood floodColor="#F4E409" floodOpacity="0.3"/>
            <feComposite in2="blur" operator="in"/>
            <feMerge>
              <feMergeNode/>
              <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
            </feMerge>
          </filter>

          {/* Inner light effect */}
          <filter id="innerGlow">
            <feFlood floodColor="#F4E409" floodOpacity="0.2"/>
            <feComposite in2="SourceGraphic" operator="in"/>
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="1"/>
            <feComposite in2="SourceGraphic" operator="over"/>
          </filter>

          {/* Line glow for dotted lines */}
          <filter id="lineGlow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="1"/>
          </filter>
        </Defs>

        {/* Central Octahedron with enhanced effects */}
        <g filter="url(#edgeGlow)">
          <Path 
            d="M197.91 231.032L223.165 243.006L244.986 285.922L197.91 231.032Z" 
            fill="#2C1A0B" 
            stroke="#F4E409" 
            strokeWidth={1.5}
            filter="url(#innerGlow)"
          />
          <Path 
            d="M196.853 229.424L246.063 179.975L223.253 241.941L196.853 229.424Z" 
            fill="#A3930A" 
            fillOpacity="0.9" 
            stroke="#F4E409" 
            strokeWidth={1.5}
            filter="url(#innerGlow)"
          />
          <Path 
            d="M224.323 243.077L297.36 238.425L247.456 288.573L224.323 243.077Z" 
            fill="#A3930A" 
            fillOpacity="0.9" 
            stroke="#F4E409" 
            strokeWidth={1.5}
            filter="url(#innerGlow)"
          />
          <Path 
            d="M224.267 242.079L247.498 178.972L297.614 237.407L224.267 242.079Z" 
            fill="#2C1A0B" 
            stroke="#F4E409" 
            strokeWidth={1.5}
            filter="url(#innerGlow)"
          />
        </g>

        {/* Dotted lines with enhanced glow */}
        <g filter="url(#lineGlow)">
          <Path d="M247 158.5V78" stroke="url(#paint0_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
          <Path d="M247 309V389.5" stroke="url(#paint5_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
          <Path d="M176.5 230H96" stroke="url(#paint6_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
          <Path d="M319 238H399.5" stroke="url(#paint7_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        </g>

        {/* Existing gradients */}
        <Defs>
          <LinearGradient id="paint0_linear" x1="247.5" y1="78" x2="247.5" y2="158.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.8" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#5F5906"/>
          </LinearGradient>
          
          <LinearGradient id="paint5_linear" x1="247.5" y1="389.5" x2="247.5" y2="309" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint6_linear" x1="96" y1="229.5" x2="176.5" y2="229.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint7_linear" x1="399.5" y1="238.5" x2="319" y2="238.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>
        </Defs>
      </Svg>
    </View>
  );
};

export default OctahedronSvg;
